snippet.title: The Devil Wears Prada 2 | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Everybody wants this. 

Meryl Streep, Anne Hathaway, Emily Blunt, and Stanley Tucci return in The Devil Wears Prada 2, in theaters May 1. Watch the full trailer now. 

Almost 20 years after making their iconic turn as Miranda, Andy, Emily and Nigel—Meryl Streep, Anne Hathaway, Emily Blunt and Stanley Tucci return to the fashionable streets of New York City and the sleek offices of Runway Magazine in the eagerly awaited sequel to the 2006 phenomenon that defined a generation. 
 
The film reunites the original main cast with director David Frankel and writer Aline Brosh McKenna, and introduces an all-new runway of characters including Kenneth Branagh, Simone Ashley, Justin Theroux, Lucy Liu, Patrick Brammall, Caleb Hearon, Helen J. Shen, Pauline Chalamet, B.J. Novak and Conrad Ricamora. Tracie Thoms and Tibor Feldman also reprise their roles as “Lily” and “Irv” from the first film. 
 
“The Devil Wears Prada 2” is produced by Wendy Finerman, and executive produced by Michael Bederman, Karen Rosenfelt and Aline Brosh McKenna. The film debuts exclusively in theaters May 1.

snippet.title: UN SUPERMERCADO DE GENTE RARA 🛒 - HELLMART [Completo]
snippet.description:
Ha salido Hellmart, un juego de miedo donde tienes un supermercado que atender de día, y vigilar de noche. Consiste en trabajar de cajero, fregar, reponer cacahuetes y procurar que nadie entre de noche. Está gracioso, son 3 horitas y media dinámicas, pero se nota que le falta muchísimo contenido. El final es por la cara. Y bueno, lo demás lo veis vosotros. Espero que os mole :D

snippet.title: SWIT EME X EL JINCHO – CALVO SOTELO (Videoclip Oficial)
snippet.description:
Calvo Sotelo no es un tema cómodo.
Y no pretende serlo.

SWIT EME y El Jincho ponen sobre la mesa algo simple: hoy criticar a la izquierda dominante te convierte automáticamente en “facha”. Sin debate. Sin matices. Sin escuchar.

Este tema no pide permiso ni busca aplausos. Señala la hipocresía, la censura social y el pensamiento único que se disfraza de moral superior.

Si cuestionar es ofender, y opinar es delito, entonces el problema no es la música.

Esto no va de bandos. Va de libertad.

snippet.title: Character Trailer - "Zibai: Mortal Flesh to Kindred Earth" | Genshin Impact #GenshinImpact #Zibai
snippet.description:
The Three Deadly Selves as specters come. In union born, in union quelled.
To hold a day as a passing year, illuminate the heart that was.
Singer: Alan

English Translation:
The moon, a jade plate, climbs the misty skies
Thin dewdrops gleam as they fall like sighs
Which grass shall never yellow in the fleeting day?
Which virtue lasts while seasons slip away?
Like drifting dust along the country way
The grass lies pale, the poplars sere, yet the end delays
By the roadside, the remnants keep their rites
As bronze statues of old lie lost in thorn and briar
All things keep their seasons, past all mortal measure
Passing through this mortal world like a waking dream
Like drifting shadows, fleeting, swift, and bright
Time races on, a white steed through the desolate plain
Its path unknown, its destination unseen
Which grass shall never yellow in the fleeting day?
Which virtue lasts while seasons slip away?
Like drifting dust along the country way
Alone with my staff, I cross the river on a single reed, like a lone wild goose in flight
Who says the river is too wide to cross?
Through shadowed reeds I seek the broken jade
The past cannot be undone, the road ahead stretches long
Friends spread the mat and share their wine, while distant fields of millet sway and shine
Some till the soil, some sow the seed — this is the life the people long to lead
In desolate courts, the withered grass sways in the moon's pale beam, and waning decay glimmers as fireflies' dream

snippet.title: Saifond Mouydhé Allah ( clip Officiel By Mintigui Prod
snippet.description:
Être orphelin de mère était déjà une épreuve immense. Aujourd’hui, après la perte de mes deux parents, l’absence se fait encore plus lourde. Même s’ils ne sont plus de ce monde, je sais qu’ils resteront à jamais à mes côtés.

Nous rêvons tous, en grandissant, de rendre nos parents heureux et de prendre soin d’eux. Mais souvent, c’est au moment où l’on se sent enfin prêt qu’ils nous quittent, laissant un vide profond. C’est la volonté divine, et nous ne pouvons que l’accepter en les accompagnant de nos douas.

Quarante jours après le décès de mon cher père, je leur rends hommage en exprimant ce que mon cœur porte depuis la perte de ma mère, puis celle de mon père.
Merci à tous ceux qui ont été présents à mes côtés durant cette période difficile.

snippet.title: The Last Goblina

When hearts break, heroes rise. From lost love to forged power, this is the legend of the last Goblina, and the tragedy that changed Mega Minion and Goblin forever.

X ► https://twitter.com/ClashRoyale/
Instagram ► https://www.instagram.com/clashroyale
TikTok ► https://www.tiktok.com/@clashroyale
Facebook ► https://www.facebook.com/ClashRoyale/

ENTER THE ARENA
Build your Battle Deck and outsmart the enemy in fast real-time battles. From the creators of CLASH OF CLANS comes a real-time multiplayer battle game starring your favourite Clash characters and more. Start battling against players from around the world!

BECOME A MASTER OF STRATEGY AND DECK BUILDING
Choose unique Cards to your Battle Deck and head to the Arena for Battle!
Place your Cards right and knock down the enemy King and Tower Troops from their Towers in a strategic and fast-paced match.

COLLECT AND UPGRADE 100+ CARDS
Hog Rider! Collect and upgrade 100+ Cards featuring the Clash of Clans troops, spells and defences you know and love and many others. Win battles and progress to new Arenas to unlock powerful new Cards to your collection!

BATTLE YOUR WAY TO THE TOP
Battle your way to the League and Global Tournaments to match against the best players in the world.
Compete for glory and rewards!

SEASONAL EVENTS
Unlock new Seasonal items like Tower Skins, Emotes and powerful Magic Items with the Season Pass and participate in fun Challenges that put your skills to the test!

JOIN A CLAN AND GO TO WAR
Join or form a Clan with other players to share Cards and battle in Clan Wars for BIG rewards!

See you in the Arena!
#ClashRoyale

snippet.title: Antonio José - Inevitable (Video Oficial)
snippet.description:
Inevitable, ya disponible para descarga y streaming:
https://AntonioJose.lnk.to/Inevitable

https://www.instagram.com/antoniojoseofficial
https://www.tiktok.com/@antoniojoseofficial10
https://x.com/AntonioJSMazuec
https://www.facebook.com/AntonioJoseOfficial

Letra / Lyrics 

Yo estaba roto por dentro 
Y apareciste a llenarme mi alma vacía 
¿Quién lo diría?

Siempre en los malos momentos 
Llega la gente bonita 
Y te cambia la vida 
¿Quién lo diría?

Tu dame tiempo que llevo tiempo conmigo 
Solo conmigo 
Tú haces que este corazón no esté partio’ 

Se me está haciendo inevitable 
Lo de no sentirme tan vulnerable 
Cuando te acercas rápido a mi boca 
Y lento te quitas la ropa 

No sé si estoy pa’ enamorarme 
Pero me miras y quiero quedarme 
Nunca he sentido esto con otras 
Pero contigo es otra cosa 
Se me está haciendo inevitable 

Ahora no puedo dejar de mirarte 
Y despertarme justo a tu ladito 
Siempre dijeron que nunca fue tarde 
Y siempre se hace tarde 
Porque estoy contigo 

Estás llenando todos los rincones 
Y calentando lo que estaba frío 
Y aquí me tienes contando razones 
Para convencerme de que sigo vivo 

Tú dime que hacemos 
Ahora que ya no tenemos remedio 
¿Qué has hecho conmigo? 

Se me está haciendo inevitable 
Lo de no sentirme tan vulnerable 
Cuando te acercas rápido a mi boca 
Y lento te quitas la ropa 

No sé si estoy pa’ enamorarme
Pero me miras y quiero quedarme 
Nunca he sentido esto con otras 
Pero contigo es otra cosa 
Se me está haciendo inevitable 

Yo no quería más amor 
Me has hecho el lío 
Así que quédate 
Conmigo otro ratito 
Tú dame tiempo que llevo tiempo conmigo 
Solo conmigo 
Tú haces que este corazón no esté partio’

#AntonioJosé #Inevitable #Luz 

@AntonioJoseOficialSL

snippet.title: Bromance Blooms on the Battlefield
snippet.description:
You and your Clan go together like a Hog and Rider, like a Goblin and Gold, like a Builder and a creepy smile. Show up for your bros this Valentine's Day and prove that true love never needs a balance change. Till maintenance do you part.

Follow us on our Socials!
Twitter ► https://twitter.com/ClashofClans/
Instagram ► https://www.instagram.com/clashofclans 
Facebook ► https://www.facebook.com/ClashofClans 
TikTok ► https://www.tiktok.com/@clashofclans

Attack. Defend. Strategize. Download for free for mobile devices. supr.cl/PlayClashOfClans

From rage-­filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

Chief, are you having problems? Visit https://help.supercellsupport.com/clash-of-clans/en/
